{
  "stem": "16395.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Majdanek [SIGHS] And I knew I have to go tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He'll leave ?] me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I really didn't trust him because a lot of people took you in and then they gave it over to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I had no other alternative.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had no place to go, I didn't know where I am.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I knew that I'm not very far from the town and I knew that there are people in the town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because while we were sitting, the Germans came in with a list, and they called out people what they need, what they needed to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I think I heard that my-- my brother was named, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Anyway, I was by this man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He brought me at night some food-- not-- not cooked food because he was afraid for his family-- but he bought me in the pocket a piece of bread, and he bought some water for the cows so he gave me some water.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told me he was gonna let me stay another day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, how is your foot?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, it's much better because I tried to stand up, and I stood already on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In trouble, it healed very fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, I have to take a [NONE-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means some things for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I found out that it's a lot of Jews and they made a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's still in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll take you home halfway, and I'll let you off halfway out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews are coming, and they are building a road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they are from [INAUDIBLE], and then they'll probably take you home.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
